---
domain: Client Learning
description: Core relationship and traversal fixture.
---

## HAS_STAKEHOLDER
  from: Client -> to: Stakeholder
  cardinality: one-to-many
  | A client can have multiple stakeholders.

## Traversal: influence-path
  path: Client -[HAS_STAKEHOLDER]-> Stakeholder
  | Follow stakeholders connected to a client when evaluating rollout risk.
